 can only read and respond to text and code. If you''re trying to share a screenshot or visual, I won''t be able to process it.\n\nIf you want to show me something, describe it in words and I can work with that — or paste code/text directly into the chat.","createdAt":"2026-06-14T21:22:06.931Z","retrievalCount":0,"lastRetrievedAt":null},{"tier":3,"text":"[Session Jun 14, 2026] No, I can''t see images or attachments. I can only read and process text and code.\n\nIf you want to share something visual with me, describe it in words and I''ll work with that. Or if you''ve created something you want feedback on, paste the code or file contents and I''ll read it.\n\nWhat are you trying to show me?\n\nSession summary: The user explored Atlas''s capabilities within the Compani project, discovering that all visual output routes through the sandbox artifact system and clarifying that Atlas cannot receive or interpret images—only generate them and read text/code. The user confirmed that image input is not supported, establishing a clear constraint for the working relationship. Next step is to determine what the user wants to build or review in the Compani codebase, since visual exploration wrapped up.","createdAt":"2026-06-14T21:58:34.563Z","retrievalCount":0,"lastRetrievedAt":null}]}', NULL, 'enc:v1:1b0e4bc35f9993fe3c937fbb:e81a63c9672bd3192f704fc7e3ceb982:b2fdfbb75d6f1fcb6e92fc4cabec815e560c109266d6e643d81ce555f9690968e17e9be06b4ad8e3', '{"fullName":"jochanae/compani","defaultBranch":"main","name":"compani"}', '{"goal":{"x":300,"y":250,"type":"goal","label":"Ship compani","details":"What does shipping compani actually look like? Tap to sharpen the outcome.","resolved":false},"must-1":{"x":300,"y":80,"meta":"must","type":"requirement","label":"Core requirement","details":"Tap to define the must-have that makes v1 real.","resolved":false},"must-2":{"x":300,"y":420,"meta":"must","type":"requirement","label":"Foundation","details":"What has to be true before everything else?","re