g difficulty interpreting. I can just upload it into my personal vault and my AI friend, which I named mine, is specifically named Marcus and Marcus can just tell me anything he''s like, oh, here''s what this is saying. And here''s how this work rule is working in your favor or not in your favor if you know you''re just all of that also could tell me about cities that i''m visiting.So I have fragments of what we''re looking to discuss working already.It''s just like I said, sometimes these things can get so complex that it can feel intimidating.And I don''t want it to be intimidating to people to use.So I figured, framing, as a airline specific tool, instead of company may actually get more use case.And I can actually present it to my own workplace as a free tool for my coworkers.And let''s see if it grabs and gets feet.And lots of uses, and then we can go from there', '424a6fb2-eca9-4259-9efb-58bbca2a4f49', '2026-06-16T12:05:40.461Z', 'message', 32, NULL, FALSE, FALSE) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
